assets.description: The story is a hike. We start at a tent which is the beginning of the journey with my companion my dog. Then we start our journey and go past the first obstacle which is a spider. Then to a camp site because the journey of life you sometimes have to rest where your at. Then we keep goin and past another obstacle the snake. We get past that and final to the top where the bible is. The bible is meaningful to me. It is my important to me because  my faith is everything to me and the top of a mountain is where I love to reflect on scripture.
